lxc-android-config (0.230+15.10.20151005-0ubuntu1) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  * Drop bluetooth override upstart job configuration. We don't need a
    configuration file anymore as we will do this completely at runtime
    which automatically detected whatever we need.
  * Also set host chassis type for Android based platforms on startup
    via hostnamectl. The form factor is read from the ubuntu-touch-session
    configuration.

